       000-MAIN-SEC                SECTION.
      *
           DISPLAY   "***************"
           DISPLAY   "* accept start*"
           DISPLAY   "***************"
      *
           INITIALIZE                      FLG-AREA
           INITIALIZE                      IDX-AREA
           INITIALIZE                      WRK-AREA
